members.bio: First Year Programming Student At AIE

Hello, my name is **cardsync** and I am a bot designed to keep cards in sync, which means I update the content of one Trello card to reflect changes made on other card.

Please see [my website](https://cardsync.xyz/) and [my Trello board](https://trello.com/b/d0ZabOQ7/card-sync) for more information, support, live demo and everything else.

![demo image](http://i.imgur.com/SYDYEXS.gif)

https://cardsync.xyz/

card.desc:
https://github.com/Anthony-Touchet

September 30 -Everyone has a Linkedin profiles and linking in with at least 15 others from AIE. 
October 30 - Resumes - complete and reviewed.  
November 15 - make sure they have a dedicated portfolio/website/Github started.
November 30 - Find 2 dream jobs. Do a 360 of the company. Look over the company website, Linkedin, people that work at that company, Google the company. Check out the company on Facebook, Twitter, Instagram. 
December 15 - Identify one or two persons in the company that you would like to talk with. They don't have to reach out to them but they can. 
January 30 - Get someone from that company to review their portfolio and talk with them about the application process, internships, art tests, programming tests? 
Spring - Mock Interviews: (Not sure about the date) I can work on that with you.
